== How to open an Incoming Port in {{gateway_product_name}} Firewall ==
For purpose of allowing an incoming connection from {{Gateway product name}}. '''Usually not required!'''

{{Firewall Settings}}

Add. Replace <code>80</code> with the actual port you would like to open.

{{CodeSelect|code=
EXTERNAL_OPEN_PORTS+=" 80 "
}}

Save.

{{Reload_Firewall_ws}}

== How to open an Outgoing Port in {{gateway_product_name}} Firewall ==
For purpose of allowing an outgoing connection to {{Gateway product name}}. Usually not required. '''[[Untested]].''' (Use [[Dev/Firewall Refactoring]] to check before and after making configuration changes if the actual firewall rules actually changed.)

{{Firewall Settings}}

Add. Replace <code>80</code> with the actual port you would like to open.

{{CodeSelect|code=
SOCKS_PORT_CUSTOM=" 9230 "
}}

Save.

{{Reload_Firewall_ws}}

